@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Home Page";
}

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>@ViewData["Title"]</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css" />
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f9;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            margin-top: 50px;
        }

        .card {
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        .main-header {
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 0;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        .main-content {
            padding: 40px;
            background-color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

            .main-content h2 {
                font-size: 1.75rem;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }

        .btn-login {
            background-color: #28a745;
            color: white;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

            .btn-login:hover {
                background-color: #218838;
            }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 50px;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="main-header">
            <h1>Supermarket Envantere Hosgeldin</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="main-content">
            <h2>Urunlerini kontrol et</h2>
            <p>Burasi senin urun panon, burada urun miktarlarini ve turlerini yonetebilirsin. Urun detaylarini guncelleyebilir, yeni urunler ekleyebilir ve stok takibini yapabilirsin.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>Supermarket Management System - &copy; 2024</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
